List files with their last-modified date

Usage: cycledit list [OPTIONS] [PATHSPECS]...

Arguments:
  [PATHSPECS]...  Paths/globs to include (default: all)

Options:
      --exclude <EXCLUDES>  Paths/globs to exclude
  -h, --help                Print help
